name: Arlen - I' ve Got The World On A String (Bennett)

values:
Merry month of May,
Sunny skies of blue,
Clouds have rolled away
And the sun peeps through,
May express happiness,
Joy you may define,
In a thousend ways,
But a case like mine
Needs a "special phrase"
To reveal how I feel.

I've got the world on a string,
Sittin' on a rainbow
Got the string around my finger
What a world, what a life
I'm in love!

I've got a song that I sing
I can make the rain go
Any time I move my finger
Lucky me, can't you see
I'm in love.

Life's is a wonderful thing
As long as I hold the string
I'd be a silly so-and-so
If I should ever let you go

I've got the world on a string,
Sitting' on a rainbow.
Got the string around my finger
What a world, what a life
I'm in love!

I've got the world on a string,
Sitting' on a rainbow.
Got the string around my finger
What a world, what a life
I'm in love!
